#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:2
msgid "查看检测历史（数据分析报告）"
msgstr "Inspection history (Data Analysis Report)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:4
msgid ""
"在主页点击 **工作列表** 进入 **数据分析报告** （路由 ``/worklist``）。页面提供 **总结**、**检测结果**、**元件** "
"三个标签页，共享顶部的过滤栏，内容区随选中标签页切换。"
msgstr ""
"On the Home page, click **Worklist** to open the **Data Analysis Report** "
"(route ``/worklist``). The page has three sub-tabs — **Summary**, "
"**Inspection Result**, and **Component** — that share the filter bar at the "
"top; the content area switches with the selected tab."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:6
msgid "**三个标签页**"
msgstr "**Three sub-tabs**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:8
msgid "**总结**：总览统计指标、不良/良品比环形图与前十不良元件柱状图。"
msgstr ""
"**Summary**: overview metrics, the good/defective donut chart, and the "
"top-10 NG components bar chart."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:9
msgid "**检测结果**：逐条列出每次整板检测记录，可进入复检、导出报告。"
msgstr ""
"**Inspection Result**: lists each whole-board inspection record; you can "
"enter review and export a report."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:10
msgid "**元件**：按元件维度汇总检测结果，支持 **全部** / **不良** / **误报** 切换，并提供饼图、柱状图与图像查看。"
msgstr ""
"**Component**: aggregates results by component, with an **All** / **NG** / "
"**False alarm** toggle, plus a pie chart, a bar chart, and image viewing."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:12
msgid "**过滤栏**"
msgstr "**Filter bar**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:14
msgid ""
"过滤栏按功能分组。除 **序列号** 外，筛选条件修改后需点击底部的 **应用** 按钮才会重新查询；**序列号** 按 Enter 或扫码即时生效。"
msgstr ""
"The filter bar is grouped by function. Except for **Serial no.**, filter "
"changes take effect only when you click the **Apply** button at the bottom; "
"**Serial no.** fires immediately on Enter or scanner input."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:16
msgid ""
"**日期范围**：**快选** 下拉（今天 / 昨天 / 本周 / 本月 / 今年 / 所有时间 / 自定义）与 **开始**、**结束** "
"日期。直接修改日期会自动切换为 **自定义**；选择预设会覆盖起止日期；**所有时间** 清除日期限制。"
msgstr ""
"**Date range**: a **Quick** dropdown (Today / Yesterday / This Week / This "
"Month / This Year / All time / Custom) plus **Begin** and **End** dates. "
"Editing a date directly switches the dropdown to **Custom**; choosing a "
"preset overwrites both dates; **All time** clears the date constraint."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:17
msgid "**识别**：**PCBA名称** 下拉选择已训练的基准产品；**序列号** 按板件序列号过滤。"
msgstr ""
"**Identification**: **PCBA name** (a dropdown of trained golden products); "
"**Serial no.** filters by board serial number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:18
msgid "**归属**：**机台**、**操作员**。两者均为自动补全输入框，会建议历史会话中出现过的值，也可自由输入。"
msgstr ""
"**Attribution**: **Machine** and **Operator**. Both are autocomplete inputs "
"that suggest values seen across past sessions; free text is also accepted."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:19
msgid "**元件识别** \\ （仅 **元件** 标签页）：**位号**、**料号** 文本输入框。"
msgstr ""
"**Component identification** (Component tab only): **Designator** and **Part"
" No.** text inputs."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:20
msgid ""
"**结果类型** \\ （仅 **元件** 标签页）：模式单选 **全部** / **不良** / **误报**，以及 **错误类型** 多选列表。"
msgstr ""
"**Result type** (Component tab only): a mode radio — **All** / **NG** / "
"**False alarm** — plus an **Error types** multi-select list."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:22
msgid "过滤栏底部为 **最大显示数量** 输入框（默认 1000）与 **应用** 按钮；修改数量上限同样在点击 **应用** 后生效。"
msgstr ""
"At the bottom of the filter bar are the **Max displayed count** input "
"(default 1000) and the **Apply** button; changing the cap also takes effect "
"only on **Apply**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:26
msgid "**总结 标签页**"
msgstr "**Summary tab**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:28
msgid "**总结** 标签页由三个并列面板组成。"
msgstr "The **Summary** tab consists of three side-by-side panels."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:36
msgid "**总览面板**"
msgstr "**Overview panel**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:31
msgid "显示所选范围内的整体统计数据，分为两个区域："
msgstr "Shows the overall statistics for the selected scope, in two areas:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:33
msgid "**PCBA**：检测总数、良好板数及占比、不良板数及占比。"
msgstr ""
"**PCBA**: total inspected, good board count and ratio, defective board count"
" and ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:34
msgid ""
"**报警元件**：报警元件总数，以及经反馈确认的 **不良** 元件数及 PPM、被 **误判** 的元件数及 PPM、每板平均缺陷数 **DPU**。"
msgstr ""
"**Alerted components**: the total alerted-component count, plus the "
"feedback-confirmed **defective** count and its PPM, the **falsely-judged** "
"count and its PPM, and defects per unit (**DPU**)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:36
msgid "面板底部显示当前查询的时间范围。"
msgstr "The bottom of the panel shows the time range of the current query."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:39
msgid "**不良/良品比 面板**"
msgstr "**Defective / Good ratio panel**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:39
msgid "以环形图展示合格与不良板件的数量与百分比。"
msgstr ""
"A donut chart of the count and percentage of good vs defective boards."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:42
msgid "**前十不良元件 面板**"
msgstr "**Top-10 defective components panel**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:42
msgid "选定具体基准产品后，展示该产品下报警次数最多的前 10 个元件横向柱状图；未选择产品时提示先选择产品。"
msgstr ""
"Once a specific golden product is selected, shows a horizontal bar chart of "
"the 10 most-alerted components for that product; if no product is selected, "
"it prompts you to select one first."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:45
msgid "**总结** 标签页同样受过滤栏 **机台** / **操作员** 过滤的影响，统计范围与其他标签页保持一致。"
msgstr ""
"The **Summary** tab is also affected by the filter bar's **Machine** / "
"**Operator** filters, so its scope matches the other tabs."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:47
msgid "**检测结果 标签页**"
msgstr "**Inspection Results tab**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:49
msgid ""
"逐条列出每次整板检测记录。表头旁显示 **显示 X / Y 行** 指示器；当匹配行数超过 **最大显示数量** "
"时，追加\"已截断\"提示，表格只展示最近的若干行。各列含义："
msgstr ""
"Lists each whole-board inspection record. A **Displaying X of Y rows** "
"indicator appears next to the table header; when the matched row count "
"exceeds **Max displayed count**, a \"truncated\" note is appended and the "
"table shows only the most recent rows. Columns:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:51
msgid "检测结果列"
msgstr "Inspection Result columns"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:55
msgid "列"
msgstr "Column"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:56
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Meaning"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:57
msgid "PCBA名称"
msgstr "PCBA Name"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:58
msgid "本次检测所用基准产品名称。"
msgstr "The golden product used for this inspection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:59
msgid "主序列号"
msgstr "Main SN"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:60
msgid "整板条码 / 序列号。"
msgstr "Board barcode / serial number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:61
msgid "拼版序列号"
msgstr "Panel SN"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:62
msgid "子板序列号（非拼板产品为空）。"
msgstr "Sub-board serial number (empty for non-panelized products)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:63
msgid "检测结果"
msgstr "Inspection Result"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:64
msgid "整板的 AI 检测判定。"
msgstr "The board's AI inspection verdict."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:65
msgid "不良元件数量"
msgstr "NG Component Count"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:66
msgid "经反馈确认为不良的元件数。"
msgstr "Number of components confirmed defective via feedback."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:67
msgid "误报数"
msgstr "False Alarm Count"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:68
msgid "系统报警但反馈为良品的元件数（报警数减去确认不良数）。"
msgstr ""
"Number of components the system alerted but feedback marked good (alerted "
"count minus confirmed-defective count)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:69
msgid "复核结果"
msgstr "Review Result"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:70
msgid "操作员复核后的整板结论，由前端按下述规则推导。"
msgstr ""
"The operator's post-review board verdict, derived on the frontend per the "
"rule below."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:71
msgid "检测开始时间"
msgstr "Inspection Start Time"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:72
msgid "本次检测的开始时间。"
msgstr "When this inspection started."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:73
msgid "检测时长"
msgstr "Inspection Time Span"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:74
msgid "本次检测的耗时。"
msgstr "How long this inspection took."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:75
msgid "操作员 / 机台"
msgstr "Operator / Machine"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:76
msgid "本次检测所属会话记录的操作员与 AOI 机台。"
msgstr ""
"The operator and AOI machine recorded on the session this inspection belongs"
" to."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:77
msgid "操作"
msgstr "Actions"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:78
msgid "**导出报告**（在新标签页打开详细报告）、**删除记录**。"
msgstr ""
"**Export Report** (opens the detailed report in a new tab) and **Delete "
"Record**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:80
msgid "列表顶部提供 **导出CSV** 与 **删除选中记录**，支持多选批量删除。"
msgstr ""
"The top of the list offers **Export CSV** and **Delete selected records** "
"(multi-select for batch deletion)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:83
msgid ""
"**复核结果（整板）**：仅当该板已被操作员复核且反馈后无不良元件时显示 **良好**；否则（含尚未复核的 AI 判不良板）显示 "
"**不良**。该口径比主页良率更严格——未经人工复核的不良板一律计为 **不良**。"
msgstr ""
"**Review Result (board)**: shows **OK** only when the board has been "
"reviewed by an operator and has no defective components after feedback; "
"otherwise (including not-yet-reviewed AI-NG boards) it shows **NG**. This is"
" stricter than the Home page yield convention — any board not reviewed by a "
"human counts as **NG**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:85
msgid "**元件 标签页**"
msgstr "**Component tab**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:87
msgid ""
"**元件** 标签页取代了旧版的 **不良元件** 与 **误判元件** 两个标签页，以单一列表呈现元件级结果，并通过 **结果类型** 的 "
"**全部** / **不良** / **误报** 单选切换查看范围。"
msgstr ""
"The **Component** tab replaces the former **NG Component** and **False "
"Positive Component** tabs, presenting component-level results in a single "
"list, with the **Result type** **All** / **NG** / **False alarm** radio to "
"switch the viewed scope."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:89
msgid ""
"页面左侧上方为元件表格、下方为图像查看区，右侧为图表区。表头旁同样显示 **显示 X / Y 行** "
"指示器。表格各列：**PCBA名称**、**主序列号**、**拼版序列号**、**位号**、**料号**、**检测错误类型**、**复核结果**、**复核错误类型**、**检测开始时间**、**操作员**、**机台**。"
msgstr ""
"The left side stacks the component table (top) over the image-viewing area "
"(bottom); the right side holds the charts. A **Displaying X of Y rows** "
"indicator appears next to the table header. Columns: **PCBA name**, **Main "
"SN**, **Panel SN**, **Designator**, **Part No.**, **Inspected error type**, "
"**Review result**, **Review error type**, **Inspection start time**, "
"**Operator**, **Machine**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:92
msgid "**复核结果（元件）**：当元件检测通过，或反馈错误类型为\"无错误\"时显示 **良好**；否则显示 **不良**。"
msgstr ""
"**Review Result (component)**: shows **OK** when the component passed "
"inspection or its feedback error type is \"no error\"; otherwise **NG**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:94
msgid "**右侧图表区**"
msgstr "**Charts (right pane)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:96
msgid ""
"**饼图**：通过 **饼图字段** 下拉选择统计维度，可选 检测错误类型 / 复核错误类型 / 机台 / PCBA名称 / "
"复核结果，按当前筛选行集聚合占比。"
msgstr ""
"**Pie chart**: pick the aggregation field from the **Pie target** dropdown —"
" Inspected error type / Review error type / Machine / PCBA name / Review "
"result — to aggregate proportions over the current filtered row set."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:97
msgid ""
"**柱状图**：通过下拉选择统计维度，可选 位号 / 料号 / 主序列号，展示出现频次 **前 10 名**。当结果被截断时标题显示为 **前 10 名"
" (基于已显示)**，提示统计仅基于已显示的行。"
msgstr ""
"**Bar chart**: pick the field from the dropdown — Designator / Part No. / "
"Main SN — to show the **Top 10** by frequency. When the result is truncated,"
" the title reads **Top 10 (within displayed)**, indicating the stats cover "
"only the displayed rows."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:98
msgid "两个图表均随过滤条件与 **全部** / **不良** / **误报** 切换实时重新聚合。"
msgstr ""
"Both charts re-aggregate live on every filter change and on the **All** / "
"**NG** / **False alarm** toggle."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:100
msgid "**底部图像查看区**"
msgstr "**Image-viewing area (bottom)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:102
msgid ""
"单击表格中任意一行，下方图像区显示该元件的 **检测图** 与 **基准图**：检测图为实际检测裁剪图，基准图为 golden "
"参考图。未选择行时显示\"选择一行以查看图像\"；无基准图时显示\"无基准图像\"。"
msgstr ""
"Click any row in the table to show that component's **Inspection image** "
"(the cropped inspection image) and **Reference image** (the golden "
"reference) below. With no row selected it shows \"Select a row to view "
"images\"; when there is no reference it shows \"No reference image "
"available\"."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:104
msgid "**导出**"
msgstr "**Export**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:106
msgid ""
"**元件** 标签页提供 **导出CSV** 与 **导出Excel** 两种方式。导出的 Excel "
"含一个数据表，以及一张图表工作表——内嵌当前饼图、柱状图的图像与对应的分类计数表（图表按导出时的字段选择生成）。两种导出均不含元件图片。"
msgstr ""
"The **Component** tab offers **Export CSV** and **Export Excel**. The "
"exported Excel contains a data sheet plus a charts sheet — the current pie "
"and bar charts embedded as images alongside their category-count tables "
"(charts reflect the field selections at export time). Neither export "
"includes component images."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:112
msgid "**注意事项**"
msgstr "**Notes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:115
msgid ""
"**机台 / 操作员 的来源将在后续版本接入**；历史检测会话这两列可能为空，空值显示为\"—\"，且按 **机台** / **操作员** "
"过滤会排除这些未归属的记录。"
msgstr ""
"**The source of Machine / Operator will be wired in a later version**; for "
"historical sessions these two columns may be empty, rendered as \"—\", and "
"filtering by **Machine** / **Operator** excludes such unattributed records."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:116
msgid ""
"**元件** 标签页的图表与表格基于同一批已获取的行集聚合；当行数超过 **最大显示数量** 时，表格与图表均只反映已显示的行（柱状图标题会提示 **前"
" 10 名 (基于已显示)**）。"
msgstr ""
"The Component tab's charts and table aggregate from the same fetched row "
"set; when the row count exceeds **Max displayed count**, both the table and "
"the charts reflect only the displayed rows (the bar chart title shows **Top "
"10 (within displayed)**)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/data_analysis_report.rst:117
msgid ""
"**子板良率（FPY）与坏板标记**：对于拼板产品，良率可在 **整板** 与 **子板** "
"口径间切换，按实际检测的子板数统计；非拼板产品的子板口径显示为 N/A。被标记为 **坏板标记** 的元件用于驱动子板好 / 坏判定，但 **不计入**"
" 复核 NG 列表，也不计入数据分析报告的 总数 / 告警 / NG 统计。子板的自动判废逻辑在 :ref:`检测设置（子板判废逻辑）` 中配置。"
msgstr ""
"**Sub-board first-pass yield (FPY) and badmarks**: for panelized products, "
"yield can switch between **whole-board** and **sub-board** scope, counted "
"against the number of sub-boards actually inspected; for non-panelized "
"products the sub-board scope shows N/A. Components marked as **badmarks** "
"drive the sub-board good/bad verdict but are **not counted** in the review "
"NG list, nor in the Data Analysis Report's total / alert / NG statistics. "
"The sub-board auto-scrap logic is configured in :ref:`检测设置（子板判废逻辑）`."

#~ msgid "**不良元件**：按元件维度汇总不良结果，便于定位高发问题元件。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**Defective Components**: aggregates defective results at the component "
#~ "level — highlights repeat offenders."

#~ msgid "**误判元件**：按元件维度汇总误报结果，用于优化模型减少误报。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**False-Positive Components**: aggregates false-positive results at the "
#~ "component level — used to tune the model and cut false positives."

#~ msgid "过滤栏位于标签页下方，所有标签页共用以下过滤项："
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "The filter bar sits under the tab strip and is shared across all tabs:"

